<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja" data-lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI/ITコンサルティング・システム開発 — ZetaX</title>
  <meta name="description" content="ZetaXのAI/ITコンサルティング・システム開発。東大出身エンジニアが完全内製で戦略立案から開発・保守まで一気通貫対応。初日にプロトタイプ提示。">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@200;300;400;500;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style is:global>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff; --bg-subtle: #f7f8fa; --bg-card: #f9fafb;
      --text-primary: #0d0d14; --text-secondary: #52606d; --text-dim: #9da5b4;
      --accent: #1a3fbf; --accent-light: #3b5fdf; --accent-pale: #eef1fd;
      --border: #e4e7ef; --border-light: #f0f2f6;
      --font-jp: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif; --font-en: 'Inter', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      --shadow-md: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); --ease: cubic-bezier(0.22,1,0.36,1);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px; overflow-x: hidden; }
    body { font-family: var(--font-jp); background: var(--bg); color: var(--text-primary); line-height: 1.8; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* NAV */
    .nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 1000; padding: 0 3rem; height: 68px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(16px); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); transition: box-shadow 0.3s; }
    .nav.elevated { box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    .nav-logo { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-right { display: flex; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .nav-links > li { position: relative; }
    .nav-links > li > a, .nav-links > li > .nav-dropdown-trigger { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px; height: 68px; padding: 0 1.1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 500; border: none; background: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .nav-links > li > a:hover, .nav-links > li > .nav-dropdown-trigger:hover, .nav-links > li:hover > .nav-dropdown-trigger { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-dropdown-arrow { font-size: 0.55rem; opacity: 0.5; transition: transform 0.2s; }
    .nav-links > li:hover .nav-dropdown-arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }
    .nav-dropdown { position: absolute; top: calc(100% + 2px); left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-6px); background: #fff; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); padding: 0.6rem 0; min-width: 200px; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.18s var(--ease), transform 0.18s var(--ease); }
    .nav-links > li:hover .nav-dropdown { opacity: 1; visibility: visible; pointer-events: auto; transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0); }
    .nav-dropdown a { display: block; padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-secondary); transition: background 0.15s, color 0.15s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .nav-dropdown a:hover { background: var(--bg-subtle); color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-dropdown-divider { height: 1px; background: var(--border-light); margin: 0.4rem 0; }
    .nav-dropdown-label { padding: 0.5rem 1.4rem 0.2rem; font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .lang-toggle { display: flex; align-items: center; background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px; margin-left: 1.4rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .lang-btn { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; padding: 5px 13px; border-radius: 16px; border: none; cursor: pointer; background: transparent; color: var(--text-dim); transition: all 0.2s; }
    .lang-btn.active { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
    .nav-cta { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 9px 22px; border-radius: 6px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; margin-left: 1.2rem; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; white-space: nowrap; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-light); transform: translateY(-1px); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .nav-links, .nav-cta, .lang-toggle { display: none; } .nav { padding: 0 1.5rem; } }

    /* BASE */
    .container { max-width: 1160px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 3rem; }
    .section { padding: 100px 0; }
    .section-alt { background: var(--bg-subtle); }
    .section-label { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.66rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); }
    .section-heading { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.6vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.3; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .section-sub { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2; margin-top: 1rem; max-width: 640px; }
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); transition: opacity 0.7s var(--ease), transform 0.7s var(--ease); }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .d1 { transition-delay: 0.1s; } .d2 { transition-delay: 0.2s; } .d3 { transition-delay: 0.3s; } .d4 { transition-delay: 0.4s; }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) { .container { padding: 0 2rem; } }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .section { padding: 70px 0; } }

    /* HERO */
    .hero { min-height: 78vh; display: flex; align-items: center; background: var(--text-primary); padding-top: 68px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .hero-bg-accent { position: absolute; width: 600px; height: 600px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,63,191,0.3) 0%, transparent 70%); top: -200px; right: -100px; pointer-events: none; }
    .hero-bg-accent2 { position: absolute; width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(123,150,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%); bottom: -100px; left: 0; pointer-events: none; }
    .hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 5rem 0; }
    .hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.66rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7b96ff; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
    .hero-badge::before { content: ''; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: #7b96ff; }
    .hero-title { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.4rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1.6rem; }
    .hero-title .accent { color: #7b96ff; }
    .hero-sub { font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.4vw, 1.05rem); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); line-height: 1.9; max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 2.8rem; }
    .hero-tags { display: flex; gap: 0.6rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
    .hero-tag { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.72rem; padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 3px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
    .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; padding: 13px 34px; border-radius: 6px; background: #fff; color: var(--text-primary); border: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .btn-outline { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500; padding: 13px 34px; border-radius: 6px; background: transparent; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25); cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); color: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); }
    .hero-stats { display: flex; gap: 3rem; margin-top: 4rem; padding-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .hero-stat-num { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
    .hero-stat-num em { font-style: normal; color: #7b96ff; font-size: 0.6em; }
    .hero-stat-label { font-size: 0.76rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

    /* OVERVIEW */
    .overview-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6rem; align-items: center; }
    .overview-text p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2.1; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; }
    .overview-img { background: var(--text-primary); border-radius: 4px; padding: 3rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background-clip: padding-box; }
    .overview-step { padding: 1.4rem 1.6rem; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border-left: 2px solid rgba(123,150,255,0.3); position: relative; }
    .overview-step.active { border-left-color: #7b96ff; background: rgba(123,150,255,0.06); }
    .overview-step-num { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #7b96ff; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
    .overview-step-title { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; }
    .overview-step-sub { font-size: 0.76rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    @media (max-width: 1024px) { .overview-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; } }

    /* FEATURES */
    .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 4rem; }
    .feature-card { background: var(--bg); padding: 2.6rem 2.2rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .feature-card:hover { background: #fafbff; }
    .feature-icon { font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .feature-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.96rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.8rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .feature-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .features-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    /* PROCESS */
    .process-timeline { margin-top: 4rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .process-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 180px 1fr; gap: 0; background: var(--bg); }
    .process-left { padding: 2.4rem 2rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--border); display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-start; }
    .process-step-label { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .process-timing { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); }
    .process-right { padding: 2.4rem 2.8rem; }
    .process-right-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.96rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
    .process-right-desc { font-size: 0.84rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.9; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .process-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } .process-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1rem; } .process-right { padding: 1.5rem; } }

    /* CASES */
    .cases-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--border); border: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 3rem; }
    .case-card { background: var(--bg); padding: 2.2rem 2.4rem; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .case-card:hover { background: #fafbff; }
    .case-industry { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
    .case-title { font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; line-height: 1.5; }
    .case-desc { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.8; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .cases-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-list { margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .faq-q { width: 100%; text-align: left; padding: 1.6rem 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.96rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); gap: 1rem; }
    .faq-q .faq-icon { width: 22px; height: 22px; flex-shrink: 0; border: 1.5px solid var(--border); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-dim); transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s, color 0.2s; }
    .faq-item.open .faq-icon { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #fff; transform: rotate(45deg); }
    .faq-a { display: none; padding: 0 0 1.6rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2; }
    .faq-item.open .faq-a { display: block; }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section { background: var(--text-primary); padding: 80px 0; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
    .cta-mesh { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 80% at 15% 50%, rgba(26,63,191,0.3) 0%, transparent 60%), radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 85% 40%, rgba(123,150,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 55%); pointer-events: none; }
    .cta-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; text-align: center; }
    .cta-label { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.66rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7b96ff; margin-bottom: 1.4rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.6rem; }
    .cta-label::before { content: ''; width: 5px; height: 5px; border-radius: 50%; background: #7b96ff; }
    .cta-title { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.6vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.35; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; }
    .cta-sub { font-size: 0.92rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 2.8rem; }
    .cta-btn { font-family: var(--font-jp); font-size: 0.96rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 15px 44px; border-radius: 6px; background: #fff; color: var(--text-primary); border: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .cta-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); transform: translateY(-2px); }

    /* FOOTER */
    .footer { background: var(--text-primary); padding: 48px 0 32px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
    .footer-inner { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .footer-logo { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #fff; }
    .footer-logo span { color: #7b96ff; }
    .footer-nav { display: flex; gap: 1.8rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .footer-nav a { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.38); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-nav a:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }
    .footer-copy { font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); margin-top: 2rem; padding-top: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

    /* breadcrumb */
    .breadcrumb { padding: 1.4rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--bg); }
    .breadcrumb-inner { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-family: var(--font-en); font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-dim); }
    .breadcrumb-inner a { color: var(--text-dim); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .breadcrumb-inner a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
    .breadcrumb-sep { font-size: 0.6rem; }

    @keyframes fadeUp { to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav" id="nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">ZETA<span>X</span></a>
    <div class="nav-right">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/#why">強み</a></li>
        <li>
          <button class="nav-dropdown-trigger">サービス <span class="nav-dropdown-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="nav-dropdown">
            <p class="nav-dropdown-label">Services</p>
            <a href="/ai-dx">AI/ITコンサル・開発</a>
            <a href="/security">セキュリティコンサル</a>
            <a href="/ai-training">AI研修</a>
            <a href="/hardware">ハードウェア開発</a>
            <div class="nav-dropdown-divider"></div>
            <p class="nav-dropdown-label">Products</p>
            <a href="/#products">自社プロダクト</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <button class="nav-dropdown-trigger">実績 <span class="nav-dropdown-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="nav-dropdown">
            <a href="/#cases">業種別支援事例</a>
            <a href="/#testimonials">お客様の声</a>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <button class="nav-dropdown-trigger">会社 <span class="nav-dropdown-arrow">▼</span></button>
          <div class="nav-dropdown">
            <a href="/about">会社紹介（詳細）</a>
            <a href="/#company">会社概要</a>
            <a href="/about#founders">代表紹介</a>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="lang-toggle">
        <button class="lang-btn active" data-lang="ja">JP</button>
        <button class="lang-btn" data-lang="en">EN</button>
      </div>
      <a href="/#contact" class="nav-cta">お問い合わせ</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
  <div class="breadcrumb" style="margin-top:68px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb-inner">
        <a href="/">Home</a><span class="breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
        <a href="/#services">Services</a><span class="breadcrumb-sep">›</span>
        <span>AI/ITコンサルティング・システム開発</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-accent"></div>
    <div class="hero-bg-accent2"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <p class="hero-badge">Service 01 — AI/IT Consulting & Development</p>
        <h1 class="hero-title">何を作るべきか、<br>分からなくていい。<br><span class="accent">一緒に考える。</span></h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">戦略立案から設計・開発・保守まで、一つのチームが一気通貫で担います。東大・東工大出身エンジニアが完全内製で、お客様の課題に正面から向き合います。</p>
        <div class="hero-tags">
          <span class="hero-tag">戦略立案</span>
          <span class="hero-tag">AI導入支援</span>
          <span class="hero-tag">システム開発</span>
          <span class="hero-tag">DX推進</span>
          <span class="hero-tag">運用・保守</span>
          <span class="hero-tag">完全内製</span>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary">まず30分、相談する（無料）</a>
          <a href="#cases" class="btn-outline">支援事例を見る</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-stats">
          <div>
            <div class="hero-stat-num">25<em>社+</em></div>
            <div class="hero-stat-label">AI/IT支援実績</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="hero-stat-num">6<em>社</em></div>
            <div class="hero-stat-label">東証プライム上場企業</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="hero-stat-num">10<em>+</em></div>
            <div class="hero-stat-label">対応業種</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="hero-stat-num">0<em>社</em></div>
            <div class="hero-stat-label">外部委託（完全内製）</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <section class="section" id="overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="overview-grid">
        <div class="overview-text reveal">
          <span class="section-label">Overview</span>
          <h2 class="section-heading">超上流から下流まで、<br>同じチームが担う。</h2>
